{"tid":264774,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【美圖新玩法】外國靚仔網紅16萬粉絲 有人叫佢露腹肌","createTime":"2017-05-31T06:07:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-31T06:07:25.000Z","uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"01f86feedcb41c94ed8ed5d78b79f62848625d6a","tid":264774,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T06:07:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170531/large/1496209909_8b45.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170531%2Flarge%2F1496209909_8b45.jpg&h=f359761c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n外國人用戶Markey於美拍擁有16萬粉絲<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170531/large/1496209910_b392.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170531%2Flarge%2F1496209910_b392.jpg&h=de8e1b1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n26歲媽媽Akashi拍短片分享化妝心得，每月收入5,000人民幣或以上<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170531/large/1496209911_df0e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170531%2Flarge%2F1496209911_df0e.jpg&h=47d00954&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170531/large/1496209912_81ec.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170531%2Flarge%2F1496209912_81ec.jpg&h=2ddcbaf6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170531/large/1496209913_edc2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170531%2Flarge%2F1496209913_edc2.jpg&h=f6cb348e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170531/large/1496209914_97ce.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170531%2Flarge%2F1496209914_97ce.jpg&h=f4dcbaa1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n近年內地興起「網紅經濟」一詞，短片分享平台愈來愈多，不少學生哥、打工仔甚至退休人士都想一嚐「做明星」感覺，周不時會上載生活短片或進行互動直播，藉此贏取人氣。商家亦正看中此點，邀請網紅於短片中分享產品，後者則可取得廣告費用。<br />\n<br />\n外國人面孔、但操普通話的美拍用戶Markey則指，年多前開始用美拍分享生活短片，目前擁有16萬位粉絲。他續稱，他從來未透過美拍賺取收入，「只是想與陌生人分享我的生活，開心或不開心，都可以透過直播或短片分享。」Markey稱，對外國朋友而言直播是較新奇的文化，他又笑言，最深刻印象是有粉絲要求他「露腹肌」，坦言只要是不過份的要求，都會盡量滿足粉絲。<br />\n<br />\n來自東北的美拍用戶Akashi透露，自兩年多前開始透過拍攝短片分享化妝心得，後來更全職經營其美拍賬戶，至今粉絲數目達到80萬。她表示，目前主要以直播示範化妝過程，因已有一定人氣，所以也吸引到品牌關注，有時候會拍攝產品測試片，「平常我在家照顧小孩，現在平均每月收入達5,000人民幣或以上，在東北來講是蠻高的。」<br />\n<br />\n記者：江靖然<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56764412&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170531\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56764412%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170531&d=syoTitLUGbK4biM2OqKsmgHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=5bf4bb44\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56764412%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170531&h=ca133536\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56764412&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170531</a>"}]}